<DATE>09/04/2009</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Sarah</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>I leased my S2000 for three years. It is a fun car to drive but it is not economical. It has power but it doesn't have much room for anything. I guess as long as you are single and are not planning to go on a trip with it, then you are ok. Otherwise, there isn't much room in the car or in the trunk. I could never get a suitcase to fit. Again, it is a great car but perhaps for college kids, who have time to drive around and are skinny enough to fit in it. I always had to watch who I offered a ride to, not everyone will fit in it.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE></FAVORITE>
